# Setters
The setters can be used to modify a map

For example, MapBox tiles on a large map:

    map
    |> setTileServer ("https://api.mapbox.com/v4/mapbox.streets/{z}/{x}/{y}.png?access_token=" ++ accessToken)
    |> setWidth 1200
    |> setHeight 800

